{"tid":117370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全城陣痛！女神波多野結衣暗示要嫁！？","createTime":"2017-02-12T07:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T07:19:06.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65bbe6a18410763c41f9f57e537a38e2b31fcec1","tid":117370,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:10:32.000Z","msg":"有「暗黑林志玲」之稱的波多野結衣是不少紳士們的心頭好，不少宅男們曾在結衣的各大社交網站下留言，稱想要娶結衣為妻。然而，近日，結衣老師毫無預警在Instagram貼出一張自拍照，亮出被戒指套牢的無名指，曖昧寫下人妻，引發網民熱烈討論！ <br />\n<br />\n6日波多野結衣在Instagram上發文，分享一張自拍美照，畫面中，結衣扎著側馬尾，穿著藍色浴衣，無名指上的鑽戒格外引人注意。同時，結衣還發文寫下「人妻」二字，並在文末標註愛心圖案。此舉一出，立刻引發網友瘋狂查問：「結婚了」？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，波多野結衣一直很嚮往能結婚生小孩，日前透露還沒有交往對象，只能暫時寄情於工作，但她熱愛工作，婚後也不打算退出演藝圈。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.gameapps.hk/images/201610/07/WF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201610%2F07%2FWF.jpg&h=b11f9b03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8fe0db618c69966fb649f66a8a0c890c3ad0a9","tid":117370,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"是撚柒鳩但"},{"pid":"238a9587287b501da65e11dfb3581ffef5201f43","tid":117370,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"新作品姐"},{"pid":"495407195a10e6c0fc8872f485ff829b89ed6f96","tid":117370,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"邊位勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ec0c5906e147d41890b1b2fb614609994865f8","tid":117370,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48c973ecc76f59bc1d8d2f8184600cce2e30091","tid":117370,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"但她熱愛工作，婚後也不打算退出演藝圈。<br />\n咁我同你結婚把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5